Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: videoscreen
Version: 1.2
Summary: play links submitted via netcat with mpv
Home-page: https://github.com/SFTtech/videoscreen
Author: Jonas Jelten
Author-email: jj@stusta.net
License: AGPL3+
Description: A small daemon which waits for incoming media urls.
        These will be played with the mpv player.
        This allows people e.g. in Hackerspaces to submit links to watch on some projector.
Platform: Linux
